Package: FlyBaseInR
Type: Package
Title: A R package that retrieve, analyze and draw data from FlyBase API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Huilin Niu
Maintainer: Huilin Niu <huilin.niu@mail.utoronto.ca>
Description: FlyBaseInR is an R package that provides an interface to 
    FlyBase API in R. It retrieve, analyze and analyze mRNA expression data 
    from RNA-seq and draw a summarization of localization data from FlyBase.
License: MIT license + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    seqinr,
    httr,
    plotly,
